title: Tech concludes day three of Texas Relays - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Tech concludes day three of Texas Relays - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: AUSTIN, Texas – The Texas Tech track and field team wrapped up Friday's portion of the 94th Clyde Littlefield Texas Relays presented by Truist, highlighted by Malik Metivier winning the 400 hurdles title
